---
import { C, FONT } from "../infographicTokens";
---

<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 720 320" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
  <title>Levers that lower AC running cost</title>
  <desc>Five levers that reduce the cost of running central air conditioning: raising the thermostat setpoint, choosing higher SEER2 equipment, sealing and insulating, regular maintenance, and right-sizing the system.</desc>

  <text x="360" y="34" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="16" font-weight="700">Five levers that cut cooling cost</text>

  <!-- Lever 1: setpoint -->
  <rect x="40" y="60" width="200" height="78" rx="10" fill={C.primaryLight} stroke={C.primary} stroke-width="1.5" />
  <text x="140" y="86" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.primary} font-family={FONT} font-size="13" font-weight="800">Raise the setpoint</text>
  <text x="140" y="108" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="600">Each 1&#176;F warmer trims</text>
  <text x="140" y="124" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="600">runtime and cost</text>

  <!-- Lever 2: higher SEER2 -->
  <rect x="260" y="60" width="200" height="78" rx="10" fill={C.blueLight} stroke={C.blue} stroke-width="1" />
  <text x="360" y="86" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.blue} font-family={FONT} font-size="13" font-weight="800">Higher SEER2</text>
  <text x="360" y="108" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="600">More cooling per watt &#8212;</text>
  <text x="360" y="124" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="600">lower kWh per hour</text>

  <!-- Lever 3: seal + insulate -->
  <rect x="480" y="60" width="200" height="78" rx="10" fill={C.greenLight} stroke={C.green} stroke-width="1" />
  <text x="580" y="86" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.green} font-family={FONT} font-size="13" font-weight="800">Seal &amp; insulate</text>
  <text x="580" y="108" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="600">Less heat gain means</text>
  <text x="580" y="124" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="600">shorter run cycles</text>

  <!-- Lever 4: maintenance -->
  <rect x="150" y="160" width="200" height="78" rx="10" fill={C.orangeLight} stroke={C.orange} stroke-width="1" />
  <text x="250" y="186" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.orange} font-family={FONT} font-size="13" font-weight="800">Maintenance</text>
  <text x="250" y="208" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="600">Clean filters &amp; coils keep</text>
  <text x="250" y="224" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="600">efficiency at rated SEER2</text>

  <!-- Lever 5: right-size -->
  <rect x="370" y="160" width="200" height="78" rx="10" fill={C.panelBg} stroke={C.border} />
  <text x="470" y="186" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="13" font-weight="800">Right-size the unit</text>
  <text x="470" y="208" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="600">No short-cycling, steady</text>
  <text x="470" y="224" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="600">runs, better dehumidify</text>

  <text x="360" y="276" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="12" font-weight="700">Lower watts &#215; fewer hours = a smaller cooling bill</text>
  <text x="360" y="300" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="11">Combine levers: setpoint and sealing cut runtime; higher SEER2 and upkeep cut watts per hour.</text>
</svg>
